2009,حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو بَكْرِ بْنُ خَلَّادٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏ وَيَحْيَى بْنُ حَكِيمٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَا:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا ي,"{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Zubair Ali Zai', 'grade': 'Daif'}","Book 9, Hadith 165",2009,,The Chapters on Marriage
2010,حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو كُرَيْبٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو مُعَاوِيَةَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنْ حَجَّاجٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏,"{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Daif'},{'name': 'Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi', 'grade': 'Daif'},{'name': 'Shuaib Al Arnaut', 'grade': 'Daif'},{'name': 'Zubair Ali Zai', 'grade': 'Daif'}","Book 9, Hadith 166",2010,,The Chapters on Marriage
2011,حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو بَكْرِ بْنُ أَبِي شَيْبَةَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏حَدَّثَنَا يَحْيَى بْنُ إِسْحَاق، ‏‏‏‏‏‏حَدَّثَنَ,"{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Zubair Ali Zai', 'grade': 'Sahih Muslim'}","Book 9, Hadith 167",2011,,The Chapters on Marriage
2012,حدثنا هشام بن عمار حدثنا يحيى بن حمزة عن عمرو بن مهاجر أنه سمع أباه المهاجر بن أبي مسلم يحدث عن أسما,"{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Daif'},{'name': 'Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi', 'grade': 'Daif'},{'name': 'Shuaib Al Arnaut', 'grade': 'Daif'},{'name': 'Zubair Ali Zai', 'grade': 'Daif'}","Book 9, Hadith 168",2012,,The Chapters on Marriage
2013,حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ بَشَّارٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏حَدَّثَنَا مُؤَمَّلٌ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏حَدَّثَنَا سُفْيَانُ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَ,"{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Daif'},{'name': 'Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi', 'grade': 'Daif'},{'name': 'Shuaib Al Arnaut', 'grade': 'Daif'},{'name': 'Zubair Ali Zai', 'grade': 'Daif'}","Book 9, Hadith 169",2013,,The Chapters on Marriage
2014,حَدَّثَنَا عَبْدُ الْوَهَّابِ بْنُ الضَّحَّاكِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏حَدَّثَنَا إِسْمَاعِيل بْنُ عَيَّاشٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَ,"{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Shuaib Al Arnaut', 'grade': 'Hasan'},{'name': 'Zubair Ali Zai', 'grade': 'Hasan'}","Book 9, Hadith 170",2014,,The Chapters on Marriage
2015,حَدَّثَنَا يَحْيَى بْنُ مُعَلَّى بْنِ مَنْصُورٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏حَدَّثَنَا إِسْحَاق بْنُ مُحَمَّدٍ الْفَرْوِي,"{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Daif'},{'name': 'Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi', 'grade': 'Daif'},{'name': 'Zubair Ali Zai', 'grade': 'Daif'}","Book 9, Hadith 171",2015,,The Chapters on Marriage